response.overview: Kim Minji, who was living an ordinary daily life, gets caught up in a confession incident triggered by the accidental discovery of the doodle 'Minjiya, I like you - Minjiga'. Feeling alienated when compared to the popular Yoon Minji and Song Minji, she experiences inner conflict.
response.tagline: Wasn't there another name? Something a bit unusual?
response.title: Love Track: Minji Minji Minji
